    cito:cites <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252148>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252149> ;
    dc:creator "Li, Yu-Long; Jin, Meng-Jie; Zhao, Jian; Liu, Zu-Yao; Wang, Ying-Yong; Pang, Hong" ;
    dc:title "Megophrys acuta Wang, Li and Jin, sp. nov." ;
    trt:definesTaxonConcept <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Megophrys_acuta_Wang_2014> ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3795.4.5> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3795.4.5>
    bibo:endPage "471" ;
    bibo:issue "4" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "449" ;
    bibo:volume "3795" ;
    dc:creator "Li, Yu-Long; Jin, Meng-Jie; Zhao, Jian; Liu, Zu-Yao; Wang, Ying-Yong; Pang, Hong" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Description of two new species of the genus Megophrys (Amphibia: Anura: Megophryidae) from Heishiding Nature Reserve, Fengkai, Guangdong, China, based on molecular and morphological data" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252148>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252149> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252148>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A: Dorsolateral view of the adult male holotype SYS a 002267 of Megophrys acuta sp. nov. in life. B: Ventral view of the holotype in life. C and D: Hand and foot of the holotype in life. E: Dorsolateral view of the adult female paratype SYS a 000168 in life; F: Dorsal views of the paratypes SYS a 002274 and 2276 in life. Photos by YYW and YLL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252148/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.252149>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Habitat of M. acuta sp. nov. in the type locality from Heishiding Nature Reserve, Guangdong Province. A: Position of an adult male individual on the stem of a plant, emitting advertisement calls at night. B: Position of an adult male individual hidden in a soil burrow and emitting advertisement calls; Ba: The opening of the burrow is small, measuring 10 mm in diameter; Bb: After opening up the burrow, an enlarged room was revealed in which the male individual was immersed in water. Photos by YLL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/252149/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

